dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.bswmoduletemplate.bswbehavior

Interface IBswDistinguishedPartition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IReferrable

    public interface IBswDistinguishedPartition
extends IEntity, IReferrable
    IBswDistinguishedPartition: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Each instance of this meta-class represents an abstract partition in which context the code of the enclosing BswModuleBehavior can be executed. The intended use case is to distinguish between several partitions in order to implement different behavior per partition, for example to behave either as a master or satellite in a multicore ECU with shared BSW code.
